配置文件
etc/systemd/system
[Unit]
Description=sidsa-service

[Service]
ExecStart=/app/sidsa-service/sidsa-service --config=/app/sidsa-service/configs/test.yaml
WorkingDirectory=/app/sidsa-service
Restart=on-failure
RestartSec=1min
StartLimitInterval=36000
StartLimitBurst=5

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target

systemctl配置文件
/etc/systemd/system



支持Systemd的软件，安装的时候，会自动在/usr/lib/systemd/system目录添加一个配置文件
软件开机启动执行命令httpd.service
在/etc/systemd/system目录添加符号链接，指向/usr/lib/systemd/system里面的httpd.service文件
sudo systemctl enable httpd
运行httpd执行systemctl start命令
sudo systemctl start httpd


